description: Get ready Houston Texas!  We can now celebrate Oktoberfest all year long with The Sauer Kraut Food truck.A tasty blend of authentic German cuisine with a Texas twist, Chef Eric brings the Schnitzel sandwich, Seigi's quality German style brats, and delicious hamburgers to Houston streets.  Don't forget to try the homemade sauerkraut or the awesome fresh prepared Spaetzle.The wait is over.  Book your event with the Sauer Kraut for Oktoberfest celebrations all year round.  Perfect for birthday parties, corporate events, weddings, and block parties.The Sauer Kraut is equipped to handle higher volumes of festivals and catered events too!Get Your Kraut on, schedule your event today!
name: The Sauer Kraut Food Truck
